    • Field Detail

      • DEFAULT_RESULT_SERIALIZER

        public static final MessageSerializer DEFAULT_RESULT_SERIALIZER
        Default serializer for results returned from Gremlin Server. This implementation must be of type MessageTextSerializer so that it can be compatible with text-based websocket messages.

      • DEFAULT_REQUEST_SERIALIZER

        public static final MessageSerializer DEFAULT_REQUEST_SERIALIZER
        Default serializer for requests received by Gremlin Server. This implementation must be of type MessageTextSerializer so that it can be compatible with text-based websocket messages.
